cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper discusses active learning in the context of deep learning for image classification and semantic segmentation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also mentions data augmentation and semi-supervised learning, which are relevant to cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), respectively.
